1
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:20,120
Grandma Pan is very healthy.

2
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:20,850
Don't worry.

3
00:01:21,360 --> 00:01:22,090
Don't worry.

4
00:01:23,240 --> 00:01:23,970
Don't worry.

5
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,360
Ah San, Ah Si.

6
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:42,560
Wait.

7
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:43,920
What are you doing?

8
00:01:44,240 --> 00:01:45,039
From now on,

9
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:47,050
you're our big brother,

10
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,360
our chief.

11
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:49,759
We will follow

12
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,200
every order you give.

13
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,259
Please accept our bow.

14
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:56,440
Please accept our bow.

15
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:58,200
No, no, no.

16
00:01:58,440 --> 00:01:59,200
I am a courier.

17
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,660
I have to deliver letters.

18
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:02,120
Brother,

19
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:03,450
please stay.

20
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:05,960
Brother, please stay.

21
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:09,039
Come,

22
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,080
Brother Jiu.

23
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:12,210
Brother Jiu.

24
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,680
I appreciate your kindness.

25
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:15,480
But I do have urgent business.

26
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:17,300
I need to deliver the medicine

27
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:19,000
and money as soon as possible.

28
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:21,360
You must know that the anti-Japanese soldiers

29
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,200
are still on the frontlines,

30
00:02:22,200 --> 00:02:23,520
fighting for our people.

31
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,760
If I arrive a moment earlier,

32
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:25,920
I can save another

33
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,760
anti-Japanese soldier's life.

34
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:29,800
Okay.

35
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:32,320
I'll return the things to you.

36
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:32,850
Brother.

37
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:35,180
Come back after you deliver them.

38
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,000
Be our chief.

39
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:39,840
Chief, please accept my bow.

40
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:52,040
Excuse me,

41
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:54,170
can I send remittances home from here?

42
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,079
Yes.

43
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:55,680
Here,

44
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:56,900
please have a seat.

45
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:02,520
Here, careful.

46
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:12,840
Are you sending remittance to Nanyang?

47
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:13,520
No,

48
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:14,820
it's for local.

49
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:15,800
Nan'an.

50
00:03:17,079 --> 00:03:17,880
Nan'an.

51
00:03:18,720 --> 00:03:21,720
You need to send remittance for such a close distance?

52
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:23,360
Is it your home?

53
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:24,800
No,

54
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:27,210
it's my brother's home.

55
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,079
Your brother?

56
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:36,760
My brother sacrificed himself on the frontline.

57
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:37,620
Only his mother

58
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:40,040
and younger sister are left at home,

59
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:41,810
with no one to take care of them.

60
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:43,160
A few of us from the same hometown

61
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,820
chipped in a few silver coins.

62
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:45,960
Can you help me

63
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,760
send a remittance to his family?

64
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:48,720
Just say

65
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:50,610
that he is doing well

66
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:53,860
and will return home after defeating the Japanese.

67
00:03:58,720 --> 00:03:59,400
Okay.

68
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:35,840
I'm back.

69
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:38,000
Dad, you're back.

70
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:40,159
My old bones are really tired.

71
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:42,159
You've worked hard, Dad.

72
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,520
It's hard work,

73
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:45,560
but

74
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:47,000
seeing the villagers

75
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,040
receive their letters

76
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,040
looking so happy

77
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,700
makes me happy inside.

78
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:52,560
Dad, have some tea first.

79
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,920
As the saying goes, "A letter from home is worth a fortune."

80
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:57,360
It truly is true.

81
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:02,240
What we deliver to them

82
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:04,680
is not just a letter,

83
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:06,200
but also a

84
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,880
bond of blood and affection.

85
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,760
It's the hope to live on.

86
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:11,760
Yes, Dad.

87
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:15,680
Grandma.

88
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,800
Why are you here so late?

89
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:20,440
Come.

90
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,640
Please sit.

91
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:27,920
Grandma,

92
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:29,480
good news.

93
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:30,800
Your son, Pan Jiu,

94
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,260
sent you a remittance,

95
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:34,280
along with some silver dollars.

96
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:35,760
I know.

97
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,200
I received them.

98
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:38,680
I am here

99
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:39,880
to thank you

100
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:41,360
for coming all the way

101
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:43,420
to deliver the remittance to my home.

102
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:45,360
Here,

103
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,040
I made some fuguo.

104
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:48,400
Eat up.

105
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:49,360
Thank you.

106
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:49,720
Eat up.

107
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,840
Thank you, Grandma.

108
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:52,040
What did you just say?

109
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:54,730
We delivered the remittance to your home?

110
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:55,920
Yes.

111
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,440
A young man

112
00:05:58,120 --> 00:06:00,850
who said he was from Wansheng Remittance Bureau.

113
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:03,160
Grandma,

114
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:05,360
what did the young man look like?

115
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,160
Tall,

116
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:08,480
thin,

117
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,290
and very energetic.

118
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,560
It's Jiadong.

119
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:14,640
Yes,

120
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:17,060
he said his name was Chen Jiadong.

121
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,780
Chen as in ear and east,

122
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,050
Jia as in nation,

123
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:21,840
Dong as in pillar.

124
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,040
Yes.

125
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:25,240
Dad, Sister-in-law,

126
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:26,520
Jiadong is back.

127
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:39,240
Hurry!

128
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:40,120
Take this box of medicine

129
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:40,960
and move it away immediately.

130
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:41,560
Remember,

131
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,840
this place has been compromised.

132
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:43,760
Go straight into the mountains

133
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:44,880
and never come back.

134
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:45,280
Dr. Fu,

135
00:06:45,320 --> 00:06:46,780
aren't you coming with us?

136
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:48,560
I have to wait another day

137
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:50,360
for the penicillin from Malaya.

138
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:51,880
If it doesn't arrive tonight,

139
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:54,409
I'll go into the mountains tomorrow morning.

140
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:03,760
Hurry up.

141
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:12,680
Who are you looking for?

142
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,720
I'm looking for Dr. Fu.

143
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:14,320
What is it?

144
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:16,640
I'm from Malaya, delivering medicine.

145
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,040
You are Chen Jiadong?

146
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:18,440
Yes.

147
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,800
Come, please come in.

148
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:20,560
Come on.

149
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:32,600
Jiadong, thanks for your hard work.

150
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:39,080
Come, hurry up.

151
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:40,400
Come, hurry up.

152
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:03,520
I'm right here.

153
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:09,360
Ajiu.

154
00:08:09,880 --> 00:08:11,080
I am Chinese.

155
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:14,320
A Chinese from Qianxi Village in Quanzhou.

156
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:16,540
A Chinese who kills the Japanese.

157
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:24,480
Those soldiers fighting

158
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:26,280
the Japanese on the frontlines,

159
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,400
many of them are actually

160
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:28,480
younger than you.

161
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,680
But to protect the country

162
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:32,360
and not be slaves without a nation,

163
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:34,320
they left their parents and hometowns,

164
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:36,179
carried guns to the battlefield.

165
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,640
They bleed every day.

166
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:38,850
To sacrifice

167
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:40,200
is a worthy death.

168
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:42,600
They are all good men.

169
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:44,320
And you,

170
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:45,680
you want me to stay here

171
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:46,840
and be a pirate.

172
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:49,130
Where is my conscience?

173
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:50,640
Compared to those soldiers

174
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:52,170
who died on the frontlines,

175
00:08:52,520 --> 00:08:53,840
am I even a man?

176
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:57,770
Brother Jiu,

177
00:08:58,440 --> 00:09:00,160
these are my honest words.

178
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:02,500
You are also a passionate man.

179
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:03,900
Which path to take,

180
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,520
you choose yourself.

181
00:09:26,280 --> 00:09:26,840
Jiadong.

182
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:28,400
Wangshu.

183
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:34,410
Wangshu.

184
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:36,050
Jiadong.

185
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:37,330
Wangshu.

186
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:39,490
Jiadong.

187
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,280
Wangshu.

188
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:41,400
Jiadong.
